title: What Do You Need To Know Before Moving In With Your Partner?
description:
Our intern Darrian is about to take a HUGE step with her boyfriend, and she's seeking some advice. After dating for a couple of months, the two are ready to live with one another.
Darrian's never lived with a man before, so what can she expect? We discuss.
